1
00:00:08,697 --> 00:00:10,028
Karin!

2
00:00:14,703 --> 00:00:16,370
I found Yuuji.

3
00:00:43,232 --> 00:00:44,221
Hey,

4
00:00:44,333 --> 00:00:47,427
why does he only draw pictures of garbage?

5
00:00:47,536 --> 00:00:50,130
He knows how it feels to be abandoned.

6
00:00:50,639 --> 00:00:52,072
Abandoned?

7
00:00:54,009 --> 00:00:59,569
Yuuji was put into my orphanage by his mom when his dad died.

8
00:01:01,517 --> 00:01:04,077
She made a promise before leaving.

9
00:01:04,620 --> 00:01:07,214
That she'll come for him when she has enough money.

10
00:01:07,890 --> 00:01:11,053
He's still waiting for her, believing that promise.

11
00:01:11,627 --> 00:01:12,423
Then, eventually...

12
00:01:12,561 --> 00:01:14,426
There's no way she'll come back.

13
00:01:16,064 --> 00:01:16,992
What?

14
00:01:18,133 --> 00:01:21,159
Yuuji was abandoned, just like me.

15
00:01:25,541 --> 00:01:27,702
Karin! My head aches!

16
00:01:28,944 --> 00:01:31,811
I always tell you, don't concentrate too hard.

17
00:01:35,050 --> 00:01:35,948
Let's go home.

18
00:01:36,051 --> 00:01:36,881
Okay.

19
00:01:38,020 --> 00:01:39,487
