Yuuji, I'm counting on you to look after Karin.

83
00:09:09,170 --> 00:09:10,100
Good bye.

84
00:09:13,775 --> 00:09:14,907
Satoshi!

85
00:10:02,123 --> 00:10:03,283
Karin!

86
00:10:04,325 --> 00:10:05,383
Karin!

87
00:10:30,852 --> 00:10:32,183
Karin, let's go.

88
00:10:36,291 --> 00:10:40,259
I'll stay by Yuuji's side.

89
00:10:42,063 --> 00:10:43,462
I'll stay here.

90
00:10:51,573 --> 00:10:53,975
To be honest, I...

91
00:10:53,975 --> 00:10:56,236
I don't think I'll ever come back.

92
00:11:01,883 --> 00:11:04,215
I'm glad I got to see you.

93
00:11:09,057 --> 00:11:10,354
Take care.

94
00:11:40,788 --> 00:11:41,846
Good bye.

95
00:12:11,019 --> 00:12:12,008
Karin...

96
00:12:15,823 --> 00:12:16,915
