108
00:14:24,986 --> 00:14:25,953
Misaki...

109
00:14:28,222 --> 00:14:31,316
I can forgive you for being oblivious to women.

110
00:14:32,327 --> 00:14:36,957
But you can't be oblivious to your own feelings.

111
00:15:08,629 --> 00:15:13,488
I'm sure Satoshi loves you.

112
00:15:14,535 --> 00:15:15,433
Really?

113
00:15:18,172 --> 00:15:21,471
It would make me really happy...

114
00:15:22,143 --> 00:15:24,322
...if you married into this family someday.

115
00:15:46,434 --> 00:15:50,461
Let's beat our illnesses together, Karin.

116
00:15:51,739 --> 00:15:52,706
