136
00:18:27,094 --> 00:18:28,288
and cried.

137
00:18:31,999 --> 00:18:36,764
But I thought you should know.

138
00:18:41,275 --> 00:18:42,542
Dad...

139
00:18:48,416 --> 00:18:52,781
Karin came to see you one last time.

140
00:18:56,290 --> 00:18:57,657
Satoshi.

141
00:19:35,296 --> 00:19:36,593
Trash!

142
00:19:41,802 --> 00:19:43,064
Trash died...

143
00:19:43,204 --> 00:19:44,637
It didn't die.

144
00:19:45,606 --> 00:19:48,541
Look, it's just sleeping.

145
00:19:48,809 --> 00:19:50,003
It died.

146
00:19:50,211 --> 00:19:51,473
It didn't die!

147
00:19:51,846 --> 00:19:53,837
Trash died.

