00:20:01,322 --> 00:20:03,381
It didn't die!

152
00:20:48,436 --> 00:20:49,366
Karin!

153
00:20:52,173 --> 00:20:53,697
Karin, wake up.

154
00:20:54,642 --> 00:20:56,041
Wake up!

155
00:21:04,218 --> 00:21:05,617
Satoshi.

156
00:21:09,390 --> 00:21:11,218
Why are you here?

157
00:21:12,927 --> 00:21:15,293
You won't die, right?

158
00:21:15,763 --> 00:21:17,628
You're just sleeping, right?

159
00:21:21,268 --> 00:21:22,860
I'm sorry.

160
00:21:25,940 --> 00:21:28,306
I couldn't tell you.

161
00:21:39,453 --> 00:21:41,853
I couldn't tell you either...

162
00:21:47,161 --> 00:21:49,721
...that I loved you.

163
00:21:54,034 --> 00:21:58,193
I loved you since I was little.

164
00:22:04,345 --> 00:22:05,835
Satoshi...

165
00:22:19,260 --> 00:22:20,887
Good bye.

166
00:22:29,270 --> 00:22:31,235
I'll be waiting.

167
00:22:35,509 --> 00:22:39,543
I'll wait forever, until you wake up.

168
00:22:43,918 --> 00:22:45,317
Satoshi...

169
00:22:50,291 --> 00:22:52,521
I'll be waiting forever.

170
00:23:07,408 --> 00:23:08,636
Karin?

171
00:23:13,981 --> 00:23:15,209
Karin!

172
00:24:23,450 --> 00:24:28,820
Twinkle, twinkle, little star.

173
00:24:29,256 --> 00:24:33,886
How I wonder what you are.

174
00:25:10,130 --> 00:25:11,597
Yuuji...

175
00:25:18,172 --> 00:25:20,766
I've heard of it when I was little.

176
00:25:23,143 --> 00:25:26,007
An illness where you can't wake up once you fall asleep.

177
00:25:29,216 --> 00:25:31,211
Once captured by the dream,

178
00:25:32,286 --> 00:25:35,585
