179
00:25:47,501 --> 00:25:49,992
I met Karin in my dream.

180
00:25:52,906 --> 00:25:55,233
She told me to hurry and go back.

181
00:25:58,312 --> 00:26:00,946
I said let's go back together,

182
00:26:02,049 --> 00:26:06,850
but she shook her head and said it was impossible.

183
00:26:14,661 --> 00:26:16,788
I think it was just a dream.

184
00:26:20,868 --> 00:26:22,192
But...

185
00:26:25,906 --> 00:26:29,041
I want to believe she saved me.

186
00:26:47,628 --> 00:26:52,721
She might be upset if I showed this to you, but...

187
00:27:13,153 --> 00:27:14,945
[ Dear Yuuji. ]

188
00:27:16,023 --> 00:27:21,314
[ I'm praying you would wake up and read this. ]

189
00:27:29,336 --> 00:27:30,998
[ Actually, ]

190
00:27:31,872 --> 00:27:34,773
[ I met Satoshi. ]

191
00:27:37,578 --> 00:27:40,005
[ Reunion after 13 years. ]

192
00:27:44,384 --> 00:27:46,215
[ Yuuji, do you remember? ]

193
00:27:46,353 --> 00:27:49,447
I'm Tooyama Satoshi, I moved here a week ago!

194
00:27:51,258 --> 00:27:53,988
[ About the first time we met Satoshi. ]

195
00:27:54,561 --> 00:27:56,222
