199
00:28:11,512 --> 00:28:13,412
and mascot girl for the aqua plants shop.

200
00:28:14,148 --> 00:28:15,380
It's a promise.

201
00:28:15,649 --> 00:28:16,907
Promise.

202
00:28:17,151 --> 00:28:21,982
[ Satoshi gave me the hope to live. ]

203
00:28:26,226 --> 00:28:28,694
Geez, what the hell?

204
00:28:28,795 --> 00:28:30,092
Great,

205
00:28:30,230 --> 00:28:31,891
one more! Ready?

206
00:28:32,266 --> 00:28:34,931
[ Even for someone like me, ]

207
00:28:36,003 --> 00:28:37,732
[ just maybe, ]

208
00:28:37,938 --> 00:28:41,374
[ a happy future was waiting for me when I grew up. ]

209
00:28:44,444 --> 00:28:49,371
[ I wanted to be by Satoshi's side forever. ]

210
00:28:51,518 --> 00:28:52,450
Bye.

211
00:28:54,087 --> 00:28:55,322
[ Satoshi was... ]

212
00:28:55,322 --> 00:28:56,223
Satoshi!

213
00:28:56,223 --> 00:28:58,418
[ ...my first love. ]

214
00:28:59,960 --> 00:29:03,649
[ That's why, on the day Satoshi left, ]

215
00:29:05,365 --> 00:29:08,424
[ to make up for not being able to tell him I love him, ]

216
00:29:09,203 --> 00:29:15,095
