220
00:30:01,588 --> 00:30:05,016
[ I'm sure we'll continue to shine forever. ]

221
00:30:05,392 --> 00:30:10,489
[ Believing we'll meet again. 
Somewhere, someday. ]

222
00:30:20,407 --> 00:30:25,840
[ But... I couldn't escape from my illness. ]

223
00:30:31,084 --> 00:30:33,145
[ That's when... ]

224
00:30:42,095 --> 00:30:49,463
[ I thought maybe God gave me one last chance. ]

225
00:30:53,540 --> 00:30:55,064
Satoshi!

226
00:30:58,712 --> 00:31:01,442
[ Only a limited time left for me, ]

227
00:31:02,449 --> 00:31:06,348
[ I had to see you, no matter what. ]

228
00:31:12,993 --> 00:31:18,055
[ I wanted to tell you what I couldn't for the longest time. ]

229
00:31:31,645 --> 00:31:34,136
Aqua plants shop, "Trash".

230
00:31:39,119 --> 00:31:40,814
[ Satoshi, ]

231
00:31:42,155 --> 00:31:45,716
[ it surprised me how you didn't change at all. ]

232
00:31:48,161 --> 00:31:49,992
Have some coffee if you like.

233
00:31:50,097 --> 00:31:51,086
Ow, hot!

