00:31:52,032 --> 00:31:54,232
[ Clumsy, and... ]

235
00:31:56,069 --> 00:31:57,798
Why don't you notice?!

236
00:31:57,904 --> 00:31:59,731
[ Oblivious... ]

237
00:31:59,940 --> 00:32:01,999
Honestly, I can barely stay in the business, but...

238
00:32:02,209 --> 00:32:04,074
it's a promise I made as a child.

