[ That's why... ]

245
00:32:31,338 --> 00:32:33,938
[ ...I couldn't tell you again. ]

246
00:32:37,911 --> 00:32:42,743
[ Because I wasn't in your future. ]

247
00:32:43,850 --> 00:32:45,545
