253
00:33:46,780 --> 00:33:49,004
[ I'm glad, ]

254
00:33:50,750 --> 00:33:54,378
[ I met you two again one last time. ]

255
00:34:03,029 --> 00:34:11,028
[ I pray that Satoshi and Yuuji will be... ]

256
00:34:12,706 --> 00:34:20,746
[ ...happy, forever and ever. ]

257
00:34:24,918 --> 00:34:27,249
[ That's why, ]

258
00:34:27,821 --> 00:34:29,947
[ if... ]

259
00:34:30,557 --> 00:34:34,822
[ you wake up and see Satoshi, ]

260
00:34:39,766 --> 00:34:42,461
[ When you see him... ]

261
00:34:43,470 --> 00:34:46,828
[ When you see him, ]

262
00:34:48,308 --> 00:34:52,408
[ Say hello for me. ]

