395
00:58:46,545 --> 00:58:51,341
I hear the crying of a baby for his mother

396
00:58:52,317 --> 00:59:02,680
I used to desire the same way in the past.

397
00:59:03,061 --> 00:59:10,159
Do I hate the person who gave birth to me into this world?

398
00:59:10,302 --> 00:59:18,063
Who created this world?

399
00:59:18,577 --> 00:59:21,307
Don't hate anyone,

400
00:59:21,413 --> 00:59:24,177
Just laugh it off,

401
00:59:24,349 --> 00:59:30,013
Even when something really sad happens

402
00:59:30,188 --> 00:59:35,921
You can pile it up as a sweet memory

403
00:59:36,028 --> 00:59:43,128
You'll know what I mean soon, I'm sure

